<item>
            <title>[LU-16675] Improve readability of testing output</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16675</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;1) The testing output can be tough to read. Adding some colors and bold text to the logging improves the readability significantly.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2) It would be helpful to have a short output that only listed the test and whether it passed. Often, I don&apos;t read the actual test output when I run a large number of tests locally - I just trust the PASS/FAIL/SKIP.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
